| Profile setup (display name + bio) | `/profile/edit` |
| Follow / unfollow users | `/follow/:id`, `/unfollow/:id`, `/people` |
| Post short status updates (≤280 chars) | `/posts` |
| Feed of posts from followed users + your own | `/feed` |
| Per-user profile pages with post/follower counts | `/profile/:username` |

**Data is stored in a database** — SQLite via `better-sqlite3` (tables: `users`, `posts`, `follows`), created automatically on first run with **no DB server to install**.

